subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Connecticut had lost to Notre Dame in seven of their last eight meetings, but Breanna Stewart delivered a career-high 29 points to put the Huskies in the N.C.A.A. title game.
